    <text>
        <body>
            <p rend="align(right)">
                <placeName>Mobile</placeName>
                <date>Dec 16/<add>?</add></date>
            </p>
            <p>
                <addressee>Revd Isaac Leeser</addressee>
            </p>
            <p>Editor of the Occident,</p>
            <p rend="indent(3)">Dear sir</p>
            <p rend="indent(4)">Our synagogue<lb/> was destroyed by Fire on <date>Thursday</date>
                last<lb/> I am hard at work <sic>endeavring</sic><lb/> to collect means to rebuild
                at once<lb/> It will be almost impossible<lb/> to raise sufficient here. We<lb/>
                expect the different congregations<lb/> in the Country to aid us. Will<lb/> you
                please make an appeal for<lb/> us through your valuable journal<lb/> to the officers
                of the congregations<lb/> through out the <placeName>United States</placeName><lb/>
                requesting them to forward<lb/> subscriptions to the undersigned<lb/> which will be
                thankfully received<lb/> I write in great haste &amp; believe<lb/> me Rev sir</p>
            <p rend="indent(7)">Yours very Truly</p>
            <p rend="indent(7)">
                <persName role="author">Imuel<add>?</add> I Imeg<add>?</add> Prest</persName>
            </p>
            <p>PS See <placeName>Mobile</placeName> Register &amp; <placeName>Mobile</placeName>
                Daily Tribune of the <date>13th</date><lb/> Inst for the Particulars of<lb/> the
                Fire</p>
        </body>
    </text>
